org.apache.openjpa.lib.log

Interface Log

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLog, CommonsLogFactory.LogAdapter, Log4JLogFactory.LogAdapter, LogFactoryImpl.LogImpl, NoneLogFactory.NoneLog, SLF4JLogFactory.LogAdapter

    public interface Log
    Logging interface that is independent of other logging frameworks.
    Author:
    Patrick Linskey, Abe White
